<view class="pay-page">
  <view class="top-bar">
    <button class="back-button" data-action="back" bindtap="onTap">‹</button>
    <text class="page-title">确认支付</text>
  </view>

  <view class="pay-card">
    <image class="pay-icon" src="/assets/icons/lock-purple.png" mode="aspectFit" />
    <text class="title">解锁完整初判</text>
    <text class="price">1 元</text>
    <text class="copy">支付后可查看完整初判内容，包括详细错因判断、7 天行动建议和下一步学习建议。</text>
    <view class="benefits">
      <text>详细错因</text>
      <text>行动建议</text>
      <text>学习路径</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <button class="pay-button" data-action="pay" bindtap="onTap">确认支付 1 元</button>
</view>
